/ subscription

h3.color-orange.bold Sign up for the latest updates
p.spacing-loose
  | Want to know the latest Hive news? Get up-to-date announcements on speakers, tickets and more.
== simple_form_for subscription, remote: true, html: {class: 'form-inline'} do |f|
  .row.spacing-medium
    .col-sm-1

    .col-sm-10
      .row
        .col-sm-9.col-xs-8.flush-right
          = f.input_field :email_address, class: 'form-control rounded-left input-lg'
        .col-sm-3.col-xs-4.flush-left
          = f.button :submit, class: 'btn rounded-right uppercase color-white background-blue full-width bold input-lg'

    .col-sm-1

  = f.full_error :email_address
  = f.error :base
end